 />\n<br />\n香港人最撚叻係打逆境波，<br />\n由六月九號打到今時今日；<br />\n由無乜人理打到萬眾一心；<br />\n由全無希望打到曙光乍現。<br />\n<br />\n請各位唔好自滿，而家嘅局面唔係不勞而獲，<br />\n喺用無數義士嘅汗水；同烈士嘅血淚換番嚟。<br />\n而我哋一班十九大學生，亦會喺接連幾日繼續為香港人提供最新、最準確狗隻動向，<br />\n令各位同路人能夠安身立命，變中求勝。<br />\n&lt;<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral%3E&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0drktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=6614677a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;</a><br />\n<br />\n想喺不久將來見證條例真正撒回？<br />\n想所有受誣告嘅義士被撒銷控罪？<br />\n想未來依然能夠光明正大喺條街，<br />\n大聲屌鳩港共正苦老母都無人拉？<br />\n麻煩各位喺呢場抗爭馬拉松繼續跑落去。<br />\n<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n自己香港，自己救。"},{"pid":"3405e8dd0e2559b2019853d49efed5541a6bd0a5","tid":1261393,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱4點check左有幾位手足企左係個邊了"},{"pid":"7620da7e9f5e82b63f69e78737b362758a088eba","tid":1261393,"uid":90306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"466d705bcaa41a1a72bc61ff90cac7ac173634e3","tid":1261393,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"而家喺嗰度<br />\n有十幾人<br />\n已經夠睇<br />\n其他人繼續上正門/後門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"沉得"},{"pid":"a75c177109a03974c68dd1d7ede2cd7c58d329a7","tid":1261393,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"466d705bcaa41a1a72bc61ff90cac7ac173634e3","tid":1261393,"uid":210794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"而家喺嗰度<br />\n有十幾人<br />\n已經夠睇<br />\n其他人繼續上正門/後門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"真係係到走你認為夠人阻？"},{"pid":"d86d57028a3e3bb062b57b63fc16c8875c9d734b","tid":1261393,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 